snippet.title: Chao Bandstand Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The 3rd place winner of the Simpleflips Music Hack Competition!

Someone has stolen the precious chao instruments for their little bandstand and poor Vanilla is stressing out! It's up to her daughter, Cream, to not only find the music boxes filled with instruments, but find who took them! Explore Music Plant Zone and make those chao happy!

Download for N64 and PC:
https://romhacking.com/hack/chao-bandstand
